Package: volrisk
Type: Package
Title: Simulation Tools for Life Reinsurance with Profit Commission
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Yoshida", "Takuji", email = "t.yoshida.science.kyoto@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides tools to simulate and evaluate stochastic scenarios of death and lapse events in life reinsurance contracts with profit commissions.
